<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Ad, marketing services cos started.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Ad, marketing services cos started.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Furman Selz analyst Karen Ficker started coverage Friday of advertising and marketing services companies WPP Group Plc, Interpublic Group of Cos Inc and Omnicom Group Inc with ratings of buy.</p>
<p>-- The three companies' stocks were added to Furman Selz' recommended list.  </p>
<p>-- Ficker also started coverage of advertising companies True North Communications Inc and Cordiant Plc with ratings of neutral.</p>
<p>((--Ian Simpson, Wall Street desk, (212) 859-1879))</p>
